{"tid":2479272,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"BLM美國三藩市教委副首：亞洲人努力讀書，係因為相信白人至上！","createTime":"2021-04-07T16:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T23:22:03.000Z","uid":91432,"like":10,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"c3d39117cc3fe90a07c34e8c94771082429d15a5","tid":2479272,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:54:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/AliMCollins/status/805474701355012096\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAliMCollins%2Fstatus%2F805474701355012096&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=4514bf77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAliMCollins%2Fstatus%2F805474701355012096&h=1b5b385b\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/AliMCollins/status/805474701355012096</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfYEJ7YwGW8yhXpgjnB2kxAeJihMYJB4qr3WYzAdVFaZC?filename=to9djoy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fto9djoy.png&h=6dee36ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>「<span class=\"red\">亞洲人</span>自以為不會遭Donald Trump趕走？你們不過<span class=\"red\">像服侍白人以自肥的黑奴</span> (<span class=\"red\">house nigger</span>)，徹頭徹尾的黑鬼 (nigger)，（白人帝國主義者）的<span class=\"red\">劊子手</span> (&quot;the help&quot;)。」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeztrfKo3bgEsbqUwYhpehWuTYURBg3jg8Qe7YGUJGwRq?filename=7HWZZnF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7HWZZnF.png&h=0621a18a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>「很多<span class=\"red\">亞洲人不相信</span>我（認為<span class=\"red\">白人有原罪</span>，<span class=\"red\">膚色判斷對錯</span>）的《批判種族論》(<span class=\"red\">Critical Race Theory</span>)，<span class=\"red\">是因為遭白人至上主義洗腦</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">亞洲人自以為</span>『模範少數 (<span class=\"red\">model minority</span>)』，<span class=\"red\">簡直是狗屁，</span>他們<span class=\"red\">融入美國</span>，不過<span class=\"red\">是崇拜白人至上主義！</span>」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRr78nupVhR5SkTBv6wX4Kx6cHZH49XSwJbQMQpc3BXTL?filename=yLgbQvF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyLgbQvF.png&h=25c2eeae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d673b0ef59966b00e31fef9860911378acc35ced","tid":2479272,"uid":91432,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:54:57.000Z","msg":"《世界新聞網》中文報道：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSu6omCsFzhG7QBc8F1Cbuoeh6FioHoA3RNFLxde8VSb3?filename=jkajZkm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjkajZkm.jpg&h=d80cd6de&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZDtvuJWR9qSFmXHF6r1BTgFqv4Ujgg5SVQqHbTXSo2wu?filename=dGPpq0p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdGPpq0p.jpg&h=59829402&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nABC報道：<br />\n<a href=\"https://abc7news.com/alison-collins-sf-school-board-removed-from-role-sfusd-tweets-vp-racist-anti-asian/10448928/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fabc7news.com%2Falison-collins-sf-school-board-removed-from-role-sfusd-tweets-vp-racist-anti-asian%2F10448928%2F&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=a822e5b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://abc7news.com/alison-collins-sf-school-board-removed-from-role-sfusd-tweets-vp-racist-anti-asian/10448928/</a><br />\n<br />\n《紐約郵報》報道：<br />\n<a href=\"https://nypost.com/2021/03/22/sf-schools-official-alison-collins-refuses-to-quit-over-racist-asian-tweets/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2021%2F03%2F22%2Fsf-schools-official-alison-collins-refuses-to-quit-over-racist-asian-tweets%2F&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=16465a47\" target=\"_blank\">https://nypost.com/2021/03/22/sf-schools-official-alison-collins-refuses-to-quit-over-racist-asian-tweet